30#if !defined(ATF_C_TP_H)
31#define ATF_C_TP_H
32
33#include <stdbool.h>
34
35#include <atf-c/error_fwd.h>
36
37struct atf_tc;
38
39/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------
40 * The "atf_tp" type.
41 * --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
42
43struct atf_tp_impl;
44struct atf_tp {
45 struct atf_tp_impl *pimpl;
46};
47typedef struct atf_tp atf_tp_t;
48
49/* Constructors/destructors. */
50atf_error_t atf_tp_init(atf_tp_t *, const char *const *);
51void atf_tp_fini(atf_tp_t *);
52
53/* Getters. */
54char **atf_tp_get_config(const atf_tp_t *);
55bool atf_tp_has_tc(const atf_tp_t *, const char *);
56const struct atf_tc *atf_tp_get_tc(const atf_tp_t *, const char *);
57const struct atf_tc *const *atf_tp_get_tcs(const atf_tp_t *);
58
59/* Modifiers. */
60atf_error_t atf_tp_add_tc(atf_tp_t *, struct atf_tc *);
61
62/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------
63 * Free functions.
64 * --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
65
66atf_error_t atf_tp_run(const atf_tp_t *, const char *, const char *);
67atf_error_t atf_tp_cleanup(const atf_tp_t *, const char *);
68
69#endif /* ATF_C_TP_H */
